\f0\b \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of Me and Santa Dying\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  Growing up Christmas was all about presents and I loved it as a kid.\
But at some point you have to start asking what the real reason is we celebrate Christmas\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 (play clip 1)\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  While some of us may or may not be confused about the meaning of Christmas, it really starts many many years before\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 WE\
\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The Old Testament is full of stories of a nation that had ups and downs.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In fact there are hundreds of pages that cover thousands of years.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And almost every story is the same\'85they start out good and end up bad and then up good, then turn around and mess up again.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And what we see is this\'85their lives are just like ours\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The times they sort of ran from God things may have went well in the beginning but didn\'92t end well for them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They can\'92t do it on their own\'85and every time they try it doesn\'92t go well with them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  They felt something that you and I feel all the time\'85and I have a feeling many of you here today feel it in some area of your life and it is this one word\'85STUCK!\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For some it is an issue of control \'96 you can fix it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is some habit that is killing you emotionally or spiritually and you can\'92t move past it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Depression \'96 and you don\'92t want to be but it is there and nothing you do seems to help it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Spiritually keep waiting for something radical to happen with God but you\'92re stuck\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Job is dead end\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a family dynamic that is out of your control\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}All of us are just like the nation of Israel in that on some level we feel stuck in some way and are just looking for HOPE to get out, break out, move out, live out\'85whatever out of our current situation!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  To make it worse\'85for them though\'85after years of being stuck\'85God went silent!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For us it is one page\'85for them it was 400 years!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See again, for some of you this is your life \'96\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve prayed for wisdom and you\'92ve heard nothing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve ask God to heal you and there is no miracle or healing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You prayed that God would just reveal himself if He was real and nothing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}GOD IS SILENT IN YOUR PAIN AND HOPELESSNESS!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are the nation of Israel in so many ways.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 GOD\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf3 Transition:  This is a different version of the Christmas story.  We haven\'92t even touched on all the stuff most of us grew up hearing about Christmas.  \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For many of us we associate all Christmas to donkey\'92s and managers and shepherds\'85and that is what happened in a literal narrative form\'85but there is so much more to the story than this\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In fact today I want to talk about the why behind the what.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to tell you a different version of the Christmas story maybe you\'92ve never heard before.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf4 In the beginning was the Word,\'a0and the Word was with God,\'a0and the Word was God.
\f3\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He was with God in the beginning.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 3\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Through him all things were made; without him nothing was made that has been made.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub In him was life,\'a0and that life was the light\'a0of all mankind.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And at the time of the birth, instead of saying a baby was born and the angels sang, John chooses to say it completely different way in so give everyone hope  that something different is coming.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 14\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The Word became flesh\'a0and made his dwelling among us.  John 1\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s so fascinating to me this is the way he choses to say this\'85the Word!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The silence is broken by God but not in the way that we think about silence being broken.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God spoke through His son at this moment\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not a self help guide on how to become a better person.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not a manual on how to live your best life now.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They had tried that for centuries and the point is they couldn\'92t do it.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t fix whatever you\'92re going through right now\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t get past whatever has been done to you or you\'92ve done\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t wash off the guilt of your past\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are incapable of moving forward for any period of time, and will eventually like you have in the past\'85come crashing back down.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The point now is\'85YOU CAN\'92T DO IT!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We celebrate Christmas not because a baby was born but because up to this moment God was silent on His plan for us, He was silent and people were hurting and wondering what was next, He was silent waiting for the right time all the while people wondering if there ever was a right time.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The Word Became Flesh!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 YOU\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Stop today and listen to what God is saying to you!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want you to pause today and listen in the silence to what God has already said!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because there are some people here today who have been waiting for God to speak to them\'85and he already has.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You might want Him to fix the situation and He is interested in fixing you\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know but I do know he has already spoken.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 16\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For God so loved\'a0the world that he gave\'a0his one and only Son,\'a0that whoever believes\'a0in him shall not perish but have eternal life.\
\
\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 17\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For God did not send his Son into the world\'a0to condemn the world, but to save the world through him.\'a0  John 3\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God says SALVATION IS HERE\'85you don\'92t have to continue to try to be a good person anymore.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have to sit with a bunch of rules that either you or someone else came up with and be good.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 He already spoke!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What he said was:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m coming for you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m not done with you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am real and I\'92m alive and you can find rest in me\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not over and I\'92m not being silent, I\'92ve just already told you what you need to know\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I love you, You\'92re mine, I\'92m yours\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This isn\'92t over\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What it means for you\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can have life\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can have hope\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can have grace\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can have what you need and more\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What to do in our place\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Give in to hope\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Start dreaming again\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Believe in a God who has already spoken to you about your future \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

